text: George Kenneth Griffey may refer to: *George Kenneth Griffey Sr. or Ken Griffey Sr. (born 1950), American former baseball player and coach *George Kenneth Griffey Jr. or Ken Griffey Jr. (born 1969), American former baseball player inducted into the Baseball Hall of Fame *George Kenneth Griffey III or Trey Griffey (born 1994), American football player
title: George Kenneth Griffey
